ime.\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy TheGood Morning Britainpresenter, 68, wrote in his new column for the Daily Express: \\\"I am not a Christian; sadly I do not believe in God (sadly, because I realise it would be a great comfort) but nevertheless I was offended by the drag queen parody of Leonardo da Vinci's The Last Supper during the Olympics opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3662946602743553e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}, {\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.979680903284217, \"rank\": 0.02074052535365265, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 1416, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.002272461536837e-17, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy TheGood Morning Britainpresenter\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"his new column\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"a great comfort\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"the drag queen parody\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\